Compiling the site
==================
cd ~/Projects/Clients/ExperimentNanocBowerFoundation
rm -rf .output tmp
guard


cd ~/Projects/Clients/ExperimentNanocBowerFoundation
nanoc view


cd ~/Projects/Clients/ExperimentNanocBowerFoundation
tail -f crash.log









Managing updates
================
cd ~/Projects/Clients/ExperimentNanocBowerFoundation
bower update
bundle update
gem cleanup
rm -rf .output tmp
guard









